h_Williams_(diver)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We felt a lot of pressure as our arch-rivals from Britain were drawn to dive just ahead of us.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2107, \"end\": 2114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9593064122351667, \"rank\": 0.04241975033252637, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They performed very well during the final.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are thrilled to grab the gold,\\\" said 23-year-old Lian.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2247, \"end\": 2251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\", \"score\": 0.9997741303129077, \"rank\": 0.00018724519908779258, \"text\": \"Lian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Before we started the competition, I felt like I had achieved what I wanted to.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I look back at my career, I can say I have done what I can to be the best diver I can possibly be,\\\" said Daley.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fencing  Hosts France finally clinched a much-anticipated fencing gold at the Paris Olympics, as Manon Apithy-Brunet beat compatriot Sara Balzer in an all-French women's sabre individual final.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2468, \"end\": 2474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9979417287686881, \"rank\": 0.002062514671127416, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manon\", \"score\": 0.999999999947704, \"rank\": 5.208045007137081e-11, \"text\": \"Manon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manon\"}, {\"begin\": 2586, \"end\": 2590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sara_Pezzini\", \"score\": 0.7881798700338024, \"rank\": 0.14425197599672296, \"text\": \"Sara\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sara_Pezzini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sara_Pezzini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a powerhouse in fencing, France narrowly missed the highest podium on the first two competition days with two silvers in the men's and women's epee individual events.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2675, \"end\": 2681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9979417287686881, \"rank\": 0.002062514671127416, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cheung Ka Long celebrates winning men's foil individual at Paris Olympics in Paris, France, July 29, 2024.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2818, \"end\": 2832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheung_Ka_Long\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cheung Ka Long\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheung_Ka_Long\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cheung_Ka_Long\"}, {\"begin\": 2877, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], 