source/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He started strongly and held off a late scare, scoring three points in a row to achieve a thrilling 15-14 victory over Italy's Filippo Macchi.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3178, \"end\": 3183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999822907920264, \"rank\": 1.6586545597454263e-05, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old Cheung clinched Hong Kong SAR's first-ever Olympic fencing gold three years ago in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3219, \"end\": 3225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leslie_Cheung\", \"score\": 0.9999999741608011, \"rank\": 2.5839097763638185e-08, \"text\": \"Cheung\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leslie_Cheung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leslie_Cheung\"}, {\"begin\": 3235, \"end\": 3244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9525601142947382, \"rank\": 0.04980215037065039, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 3245, \"end\": 3248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_administrative_regions_of_China\", \"score\": 0.9999579235648793, \"rank\": 4.207746015404247e-05, \"text\": \"SAR\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_administrative_regions_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_administrative_regions_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 3302, \"end\": 3307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999730734070208, \"rank\": 0.0002693367